snippet.title: Amber Heard Is In SERIOUS TROUBLE Due To New Evidence | The Gossipy
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Is In Serious Trouble Due To Johnny Depp's New Evidence | The Gossipy

Welcome toThe Gossipy. We make interesting videos about Hollywood in English. We give you a closer look in the lives of celebrities like Kanye West, Ed Sheeran, The Rock, Jay Z, Selena Gomez, Kylie Jenner, Kim Kardashian, Rihanna and 100s more.

For 5 years now, Johnny Depp and his ex-wife Amber Heard have been jawing back and forth at each other to get an advantage in court on numerous cases that have been filed by them at each other. 

Johnny Depp filed a Defamation Suit against Heard for $50 million and she filed a countersuit worth $100 million. That case is still going on and has been delayed until 2022 due to the pandemic pushing back scheduling. 

But even though that’s going on, there are some things that aren’t adding up in Heard’s defense. Especially, with the new Bodycam footage
